          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-235-035F-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="large-writing">Beneath</hi> this verdant Hillock lies,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-035F-line-2" n="2">Demar the Wealthy, and the Wise.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-035F-line-3" n="3">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-035F-line-4" n="4">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-035F-line-5" n="5">His Heirs, that he might safely rest,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-035F-line-6" n="6">Have put his Carcase in a Chest;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-035F-line-7" n="7">The very Chest, in which they say,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-035F-line-8" n="8">His other Self, his Money lay.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-035F-line-9" n="9">And if his Heirs continue kind</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-035F-line-10" n="10">To that dear Self he left behind,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-035F-line-11" n="11">I dare believe, that Four in Five</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-035F-line-12" n="12">Will think his better Self alive.</l>
          </lg>
